<L>__{interior frank's van minutes later}
<A>__{at an intersection... they see a "detour" sign. frank and lana exchange concerned looks. frank turns the corner. the van starts vibrating violently, tossing them around.}
<C>__{ned}
<P>__{(checks his watch)}
<D>__{we're not going to make it.}
<C>__{frank}
<D>__{we'll make it!}
<A>__{he shifts gears, guns the engine. they rocket ahead, bouncing wildly, their heads thumping the car roof! the van splashes through deep water, a huge fantail spraying out on both sides.}
